'''Katherine Soucie''' (November 18, 1953) is an American voice actress. She played [[Goldberry]], [[Angelica Baggins|Angelica]] and [[Arwen]] in the game ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring (video game)|The Fellowship of the Ring]]'' (but only appeared on the credits for the first) and did additional voices for ''[[The Hobbit (2003 video game)|The Hobbit]]''.
